==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Text-book
<hw>Text"-book`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A book
with wide spaces between the lines, to give room for notes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A volume, as of some classical author, on which a
teacher lectures or comments; hence, any manual of instruction; a
schoolbook.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

